    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pieces of cloth that are used to envelop the hands of the celebrant when holding the monstrance during the Benediction of the Blessed Sacrament and on other occasions. It takes the place of the humeral veil, which is also used for this purpose.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
